{"tid":1223361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［例行親子活動］星期日大遊行 窩心小提示","createTime":"2019-06-14T16:30:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T02:30:40.000Z","uid":136958,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4a9cb859d97c56055b0c230d6fb2c8963435f520","tid":1223361,"uid":136958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T16:30:06.000Z","msg":"黎緊16/6 <span style=\"font-size: large;\">立法會冇人冇會</span> 所以準備帶一家大細出去呢個老少咸宜既活動<span style=\"font-size: large;\">和你飛一天</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想各位一齊準備下 有咩小貼士<br />\n<br />\n1. 廢物天文台 預測 26度-31度 略熱 要補充水分及充足睡眠<br />\n<br />\n2. 嗰日有機會有驟雨 帶定一兩把遮 以防不時之需<br />\n<br />\n3. 可以響應舉辦者 著上黑色透氣衣服 表達對政府既不滿<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎帶同長輩既各位補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51d27759805c62a7f6632107d0e0b20de8015656","tid":1223361,"uid":113512,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:30:40.000Z","msg":"記得自行帶走垃圾<br />\n幾十萬人留低大量垃圾會俾人汙名化"}]}